OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773933104
OL,3,CWhy the Bank of England says inflation
OL,4,Cis rising again
OL,6,FBased on oil and gas price movements
OL,7,Fcaused by US President Donald Trump's
OL,8,Fwar so far, and gathered evidence, the
OL,9,FBank of England now expects inflation
OL,10,Fto be about 1 percentage point higher
OL,11,Fthan it would otherwise have been in
OL,12,Fthe third quarter of this year.
OL,14,FThe expectations it had in February
OL,15,Fthat inflation would gradually fall to
OL,16,Fthe target in the coming six months
OL,17,Fhave been wiped out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
