OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773933104
OL,3,CWhy the Bank of England says inflation
OL,4,Cis rising again
OL,6,FIt is striking that every member of
OL,7,Fthe Bank's MPC voted to maintain the
OL,8,Fpolicy interest rate at 3.75%, because
OL,9,Fright now they all fear the
OL,10,Finflationary effect of the war more
OL,11,Fthan they do the shock to business and
OL,12,Fconsumer confidence and the inevitable
OL,13,Frecessionary impact.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
